{"tid":2425856,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"納瓦爾尼傳被送「最殘酷」勞改營","createTime":"2021-02-27T15:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T15:17:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12c915f1477b73b4c0b493ce20f52003a4eef483","tid":2425856,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T15:17:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210227/H5YVOQYPEJGXND26GTGQTWZOQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210227%2FH5YVOQYPEJGXND26GTGQTWZOQY%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm9C8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=bf871e37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210227%2FH5YVOQYPEJGXND26GTGQTWZOQY%2F&h=e5849fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210227/H5YVOQYPEJGXND26GTGQTWZOQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n納瓦爾尼傳被送「最殘酷」勞改營<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Gap7xaGT0hXQdxzSNUF459ugsSk=/1372x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KM6PDRGZ2FC2ZCT5IADKXHBZ2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGap7xaGT0hXQdxzSNUF459ugsSk%3D%2F1372x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKM6PDRGZ2FC2ZCT5IADKXHBZ2I.jpg&h=f70b7103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n納爾瓦尼<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯反對派領袖納瓦爾尼近日突然從監獄消失，俄羅斯聯邦監獄局昨證實已轉送他到另一「拘留中心」，但拒絕透露具體位置，估計他正被送往勞改營。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關無窗火車運送<br />\n<br />\n納瓦爾尼早前被判監逾兩年，關押在莫斯科的馬特羅斯卡雅蒂什納監獄。但其律師科布澤夫前日探訪他時，獲告知他已離開，但沒透露去向，估計他最有可能被送往勞改營，但也可能是其他地方。根據俄羅斯法例，納瓦爾尼可被送入莫斯科附近勞改營，地點較可能是莫斯科以東240公里的弗拉基米爾（Vladimir），有關注囚犯權益人士形容那裏是「最殘酷」的地區。他前往勞改營過程估計亦慘無人道，因為囚犯一般會被關在無窗的火車卡內，分開數次運送，可花上數星期，其間不得聯絡家人和律師，整個制度與前蘇聯迫害政治犯的手法同出一轍。<br />\n<br />\n自納瓦爾尼上月被捕後，各界都十分關注他的安危，..............................「納瓦爾尼不知所終，就證明了他的處境有多危險」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》"}]}